definitions.definition: In an unsteady manner, so as to shake or falter .
examples: He climbed the stairs unsteadily , grasping the banister and gasping for breath.

definitions.definition: In an uncertain manner; with hesitation or timidity .

main_definition: In an unsteady manner, so as to shake or falter .
secondary_definitions: In an uncertain manner; with hesitation or timidity .
